{"tid":250753,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[Steam][Survival] Infestation: The New Z","createTime":"2017-05-20T10:30:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-31T17:36:29.000Z","uid":39087,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9e9d0d4d3ec45e95e4a199122dcb1f9764a7a106","tid":250753,"uid":39087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T10:30:15.000Z","msg":"官網: <a href=\"http://playnewz.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fplaynewz.com%2F&d=APk9rvMsCVL9feuIhYiW0iwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=44c453d5\" target=\"_blank\">http://playnewz.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而家有港SER 加上新開AC 送一星期Premium  3-5PING咋!</span></span><br />\n <br />\nSteam link: <a href=\"http://store.steampowered.com/app/555570/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F555570%2F&d=APk9rvMsCVL9feuIhYiW0iwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=7723b261\" target=\"_blank\">http://store.steampowered.com/app/555570/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: navy;\">簡介: </span></strong><br />\n<br />\nInfestation: The New Z 係一隻一款殭屍生存大型多人開放世界遊戲，<span style=\"color: red;\">玩家同玩家之間嘅對戰係呢隻遊戲嘅重點，唔存在要周圍執食物去透爐BBQ嘅玩法</span>，因為好難餓死。<br />\n<br />\nWar Z 係呢隻遊戲嘅前身，經過唔同版本嘅演替出 Infestation: The New Z。前者飽受穿牆自描外掛困擾，後者<span style=\"color: red;\">防外掛系統比較完善</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: navy;\">課金問題:</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n呢隻遊戲課金唔會令你勁啲，課金亦主要買 Premium account<br />\n<br />\nPremium account 主要有以下作用:<br />\n<br />\n1. 人物死左即刻復活唔洗比錢 or 等時間 （你亦可以等3分鐘 or 比 ＄15000 遊戲幤復活）<br />\n2. 每日送禮物（睇你運氣，通常垃圾）<br />\n3. 雙經雙錢<br />\n<br />\n由於經常都有雙倍點數嘅活動，課金亦都相當抵<br />\n呢加黎講 40 HKD ＝ 4個月 Premium account<br />\n<br />\n一齊玩嘅有人課金亦有人冇課金<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: navy;\">特點:</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n1. Global Inventory<br />\n<br />\n係遊戲世界執完野（死會跌裝），可以登出伺服器，擺係大廳嘅Global Invetory （留返下次用）<br />\n<br />\n2. Skill Tree<br />\n<br />\n殺人 or 殺殭屍會攞到經驗值，經驗值可以用黎升級自己隻人物，例如冇咁易比殭屍察覺，瞄準器會再準啲之類。長玩嘅遲早都會升哂，但我地一班長玩嘅都未升哂，所以都算耐玩。<br />\n<br />\n3. Skin<br />\n<br />\nSkin 唔會有數值加成，係令呢隻遊戲耐玩度增加嘅其中一個因素。唔少 Skin 係會發哂光咁，一來型，二來招搖，變相會係地圖報自己位，對於有實力嘅人黎講，會無形中道出四字真言 : 夠做埋黎。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: navy;\">開心玩 Gameplay</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w39xGgi_Yek\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dw39xGgi_Yek&d=APk9rvMsCVL9feuIhYiW0iwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=d3b6637d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w39xGgi_Yek</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有興趣一齊玩歡迎入黎RC <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nRC: 26397891 （活躍玩家暫時6-7人） <br />\n<br />\n有咩問題都可以入黎問</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"f4cc21132d1e9a026862deacb439cdbf9f2f9d9e","tid":250753,"uid":39087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T10:30:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: navy;\"><strong>新朋友注意事項:</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n1. 盡量用近戰武器打殭屍，用槍會暴露自己位置<br />\n<br />\n2. 夜晚請帶夜視鏡<br />\n<br />\n3. 最好聯群結黨（2-3人）去執物資，安全啲<br />\n<br />\n4. 所有食物可以唔洗刻意執，肚餓只會扣血，唔會死<br />\n<br />\n5. 主要執步槍，e.g. M4A1, SIG556, L85, HONEY BADGER<br />\n<br />\n6. 唔等洗嘅步槍可以拆左排彈匣出黎，大部分彈匣都通用於其他步槍<br />\n<br />\n7. 敵人未發現你可以試下行近啲先殺，易爆頭，一兩粒足以收頭<br />\n<br />\n8. 善用藥物，盡量保持滿血，以免被收皮，建議藥物放快捷鍵<br />\n<br />\n9. 善用盾 (Riot Shield/Wood Shield) 擋子彈，保護自己，建議盾放快捷鍵<br />\n<br />\n10. 避免用錢復活角色同係商城買野，錢可儲起同其他玩家交易商城嘅野(平啲) or Skin<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: navy;\">新手過來人有感:</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n開始果陣比人虐待真係幾慘 <br />\n雖然我呢加都係，但情況有好轉 <br />\n<br />\n呢隻遊戲嘅真理就係要埋堆 <br />\n三五成群出去冧友搶裝 <br />\n唔小心奉獻左性命 <br />\n就轉個頭返入去覆灼 <br />\n<br />\n如果覺得玩到冇目標 <br />\n短期黎講緊係要儲齊彈藥 <br />\n同人開片至少都準備好頭盔呀，盔甲呀，槍啦大佬 <br />\n長遠黎講我想虐待返其他人 <br />\n<br />\n唔好灰心！堅持！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: navy;\">Q&amp;A</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nQ: 唔課金玩得唔得<br />\nA: 得。<br />\n<br />\nQ: 車點用？<br />\nA: 車只可以係 Beginner Server / Premium Server / Private Server 用，對住部車按實 F5 可以收返部車。<br />\n<br />\nQ: 我得一個人，可以點玩？<br />\nA: 可以簡啲最少人嘅 Server，因為呢啲 Server 都係單人出團勝地，你得一個時人地都係得一個，自己安全執下野咁。<br />\n<br />\nQ: Beginner Server 可以玩幾耐？<br />\nA: 72 Hours<br />\n<br />\nQ: 點入 Official Server？<br />\nA: 係 Beginner Server 生存 1 Hour"},{"pid":"f31090b4bb2f5229018ea153cecfdc9f81960f7f","tid":250753,"uid":39087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T14:30:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fefc782d3e81118e36525861b57fb33e8bd4fef","tid":250753,"uid":39087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T12:11:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"491af8f29b7eb290724e86ca0672bfa19424e96f","tid":250753,"uid":6718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T13:01:24.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"38b7bbdcd77de33cc30b5ccc85c905333fcd439b","tid":250753,"uid":39087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T13:31:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eca379e010a059a18a8f1d7c378ceb42e2be82b9","tid":250753,"uid":6718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T18:53:07.000Z","msg":"邊到有車揸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a8c0613c3b97ffe032a024d66c1a56da111c217","tid":250753,"uid":39087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T11:19:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊到有車揸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要搵 同得私ser premium 先用得 搵唔到就入rc group搵人車你 入面全部人都有車"},{"pid":"3f7e81feb8028d54116631fbf54f21ff7e064803","tid":250753,"uid":6718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T12:26:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>邊到有車揸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要搵 同得私ser premium 先用得 搵唔到就入rc group搵人車你 入面全部人都有車</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n搵咗半個map 都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceb39042dcf19ed87718a328d1985fe90cbab7b0","tid":250753,"uid":6718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T12:27:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>邊到有車揸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要搵 同得私ser premium 先用得 搵唔到就入rc group搵人車你 入面全部人都有車</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n搵咗半個map 都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nBeginner 無？"},{"pid":"5aa2bd024b470d650eaac74d803ce7d7b6eefd14","tid":250753,"uid":39087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T08:18:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>邊到有車揸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要搵 同得私ser premium 先用得 搵唔到就入rc group搵人車你 入面全部人都有車</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n搵咗半個map 都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nBeginner 無？</blockquote><br />\n你入黎rc 問下佢地 有咩唔明 問得架啦 係beginner official ser冇得用車 但有得搵車 佢架車唔係就咁spawn 出黎 係一個好似riot shield 道具咁既樣 但隻色好明顯 你當車係道具咁啦"},{"pid":"037cf073b3df0f51606be98a28e2a508cb13deb1","tid":250753,"uid":39087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T13:41:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d65d87d97a842d79c22d08f23c36deff30e9fce","tid":250753,"uid":39087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T05:04:01.000Z","msg":"又有雙倍點數活動啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  而家34$HKD 玩到4個月會員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 加上有團員準備開